Now you can swap which image displays as your NFB! Each NFB now includes an original gif, a glitched gif, and PFP(Skullaroid)! A few other NFBs have even more like the destination gif & Skullrivative gifs!
[nahfungiblebones.com/view](https://nahfungiblebones.com/view)

First of its kind animated & swappable displayed image NFT series

It includes 10,005 randomly generated NFTs that rest in peace on the ETH Blockchain.

- 767 Unbroken
- 21 OG Rare
- 10 Infinity Rare
- 3 Cr8zy Rare

Created by [Trevor Van Meter](https://www.heytvm.com) and pals
